---
title: Bulgogi Burger and Sticky Bulgogi Chicken  with Wedges and Sriracha Dressed Asian Style Salad
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, this tasty Bulgogi Burger and Sticky Bulgogi Chicken is perfect for a casual sharing-style dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R34_W42_UK_SSF3777-6_MAIN_F3_low-6a2d03fe.jpg
